text: Vyshinsky (, ) is the Russian and Ukrainian form of the Polish family name Wyszyński. It corresponds with the Lithuanian name Višinskis. Notable people with the surname include: *Andrey Yanuaryevich Vyshinsky (1883–1953), Soviet politician, jurist and diplomat *Kirill Valeryevich Vyshinsky (born 1967), Ukrainian and Russian journalist Category:Russian-language surnames
title: Vyshinsky (surname)
